item.description: Imagine...an entire weekend to work on your family albums! Come to my Creative Memories Crop Away Weekend and enjoy [u]6 feet of cropping space[/u], inspiration, ideas, drawings, exclusive goodie bag, fun, and of course, completed pages! Space is limited, so sign up TODAY! Come Crop Away from 6:00pm Friday, September 30th, until 6:00pm Sunday, October 2nd, 2011! You owe it to yourself...and your family! $169.00 Prepaid Only (includes breakfast, lunch & dinner on Saturday and breakfast & lunch on Sunday, plus snacks throughout the weekend)
